SUMMARY:Cynthia Brothers and Shannon Koyano Present: The Vanishing Seattle Variety Show
DESCRIPTION:WEDS May 20thDOORS 7:30pm / 8pm SHOW21+$15 ADV/$18 DOSIts another edition of the Vanishing Seattle Variety Show! With fabulous guests: drag legend and former Miss Gay Seattle Cookie Couture\, and writers/music journalists Martin Douglas s Cobain 50 podcast! Plus comedy from Shannon Koyano\, Vanishing Seattle trivia\, and special prizes and Seattle-themed drinks created by the citys best bartender\, Ramona! The VSVS is a one-of-a-kind event featuring all-local talent and blending stand-up comedy\, storytelling\, dazzling drag\, and more – in tribute to the wild and weird Seattle you once knew (or still do)!**Get your tix early for this sell-out show**Co-hosted by Vanishing Seattle founder Cynthia Brothers and longtime local comic Shannon Koyano. doors 7:30pm – get there early for award-winning @steviesfamous pizza!
